name: Snake Eyes
overview: Published in the SEUCK Compo 2019 / a.k.a. "Illinois Jones" You are adventurer Illinois Jones. You were out on an adventure until you got lost. You now have a simple but complex mission, in which is to go through the dangerous depths of the freaky jungle. Then you must make your way through the dangerous temple of snakes. Knowing Illinois Jones, he likes to be quite greedy, and he decides to try and make himself a rich man. Unfortunately if he is to find treasure, and gems, he has to face a few challenges on the way. Luckily, he has his own secret weapon. He can only shoot it upwards. Help Illinois reach home - Can you help him return home and be awarded the rank of Snake Eyes? Can you adventure on further and beat the mini game "Baby Snakes," joining the Snake Eyes Elite?
